Random artists from random countries and sorted by various categories to display.Grid cards by:  Liked, followers, comments, views, new/recents, country, random art, random artists
3-4X in one row for each test.

<%= render partial: 'shared/banner'  %>


<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
  <h3>Explore art all around the world</h3>
  <h3>Click a country on the map or search</h3>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
   <%= link_to "Browse Art", browse_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
  </div>
</div>

 <%= simple_form_for(:country, as: :select2, method: :get, url: '/artists_countries') do |f| %>
  <%= f.input :country, as: :select2, collection: CountryStateSelect.countries_collection.sort %>
  <%= f.submit %>
<% end %>

<div

  id="map"
  style="width: 100%;
  height: 600px;"
  data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
  data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>"

></div>


Grid test I to generate random artists.

<div class="container">
  <% @artists.sample(3).each do |artist| %>
